OL,3,CJersey schoolchildren learn the
OL,4,Ctraditional values of a Victorian
OL,5,CChristmas
OL,7,FDid you know many of today's favourite
OL,8,FChristmas traditions were popularised
OL,9,Fby the Royal family in the 19th
OL,10,Fcentury? From presents to puddings and
OL,11,Fcrackers to cards.
OL,13,FIn the late 1800s, Queen Victoria and
OL,14,FPrince Albert inspired many of the
OL,15,Ftraditions practised across the world
OL,16,Ftoday.
