OL,7,FAlice Honey, the Education Officer for
OL,8,FJersey Heritage said: "We are making
OL,9,Ftraditional Victorian crafts with
OL,10,Fthem, so we've got our paper cone that
OL,11,FVictorians would have put trinkets and
OL,12,Fgifts in and we're making pomanders as
OL,13,Fwell - with oranges and cloves.
OL,15,F"We're also having a go at writing
OL,16,Fwith dip pens as well which Victorian
OL,17,Fpeople would have been using at
OL,18,Fschool."
