OL,7,F"In the Victorian era, they probably
OL,8,Fwouldn't have been in school at their
OL,9,Fage, or there would certainly be no
OL,10,Fissue for them ducking out of school.
OL,12,F"They all seemed really happy when I
OL,13,Fsuggested they are going to do 14-hour
OL,14,Fdays stuck up a chimney scrubbing
OL,15,Fsomeone's floor."
