OL,4,Ctraditional values of a Victorian
OL,5,CChristmas
OL,7,FThe schoolchildren said they learnt a
OL,8,Flot about traditional Christmas
OL,9,Fvalues; from the origins of the humble
OL,10,FChristmas card, to puckering up under
OL,11,Fa plant, the classes really did
OL,12,Fcapture their imagination.
OL,14,FSo much so, that one pupil even said
OL,15,Fthey would have been happy to have
OL,16,Fgrown up in the Victorian era.
